ActTransportation of Dangerous Goods Act, 1992
SubjectRegulations Amending the Transportation of Dangerous Goods Regulations (Formatting Changes)
PrecisRegulations amending the TRANSPORTATION OF DANGEROUS GOODS REGULATIONS (FORMATTING CHANGES) (TDGR) in order to revise the TDGR format to be consistent with the Department of Justice formatting standards and ensure that an official consolidated version of the TDGR is easily accessible to all Canadians on the Justice Laws Website.
